high_descs: Turn and walk left to the bed.
Pick up a striped pillow from the bed.
Turn left to walk to the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Look at a striped pillow under a lit lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the bed.
Pick up the striped pillow from the left side of the bed.
Turn around and walk to the small wooden nightstand with the lamp by the window.
anns.task_desc: Examine a pillow by the light of a small lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and take step to your right then walk to the bed.
Pick up the pillow that's in front of you on the bed.
Turn right and take two steps to your right then walk to the lamp that's on the night stand.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a pillow by lamp light.
